            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Cremonio Albuci <expan><abbr>fi</abbr><ex>lio</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Aulino immatura <lb n="3"/>aetate decepto <expan><abbr>q</abbr><ex>ui</ex></expan> vi<lb break="no" n="4"/>xit <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> XII et Vinicio <lb n="5"/>Ingenui filio Aulino <lb n="6"/>prima aetate <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">decepto</supplied> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>q</abbr><ex>ui</ex></expan> vixit an<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>os</ex></expan></supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="8"/>Vibia Mater<supplied reason="lost">na filiis</supplied> <lb n="9"/>piissimi<supplied reason="lost">s et dul</supplied><lb break="no" n="10"/>cissim<supplied reason="lost">is fecit</supplied> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Cremonio Albucio <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>decur</abbr><ex>ioni</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Vint</abbr><ex>iensium</ex></expan> IIvira<supplied reason="lost">li</supplied> <lb n="3"/>sacerdotali et om<lb break="no" n="4"/>nibus honoribus fu<lb break="no" n="5"/>ncto Vibia Mater<lb break="no" n="6"/>na marito incom<lb break="no" n="7"/>parabili fecit
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): CIL: Z. 12: dec(urioni) Eingemeißelt (capitalis rustica). Bearbeiterin: V. Pettirossi.</p>
            </div>
